{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1430,"text":"Good evening."}]},{"cues":[{"time":2474,"text":"We are in this wonderful"},{"time":4409,"text":"open-air amphitheater"},{"time":6289,"text":"and we are enjoying ourselves"},{"time":8043,"text":"in that mild evening"},{"time":9745,"text":"temperature tonight,"},{"time":11033,"text":"but when Qatar will host"},{"time":15350,"text":"the football World Cup"},{"time":16892,"text":"10 years from now,"},{"time":18737,"text":"2022,"},{"time":20209,"text":"we already heard it will be"},{"time":21441,"text":"in the hot, very hot and sunny"},{"time":25089,"text":"summer months of June and July."},{"time":27433,"text":"And when Qatar has been assigned"},{"time":29746,"text":"to the World Cup all, many"},{"time":31377,"text":"people around the world have been"},{"time":33278,"text":"wondering, how would it be"},{"time":34629,"text":"possible that football players"},{"time":36852,"text":"show spectacular football,"},{"time":39013,"text":"run around in this desert"},{"time":40218,"text":"climate? How would it be"},{"time":41749,"text":"possible that spectators sit,"},{"time":44644,"text":"enjoy themselves in open-air"},{"time":47636,"text":"stadia in this hot environment?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":50845,"text":"Together with the architects of"},{"time":52486,"text":"Albert Speer &amp; Partner, our engineers"},{"time":54428,"text":"from Transsolar have been"},{"time":56284,"text":"supporting, have been developing"},{"time":58068,"text":"open-air stadia based on 100 percent"},{"time":61731,"text":"solar power, on 100 percent solar cooling."}]},{"cues":[{"time":66165,"text":"Let me tell you about that,"},{"time":67572,"text":"but let me start with comfort."},{"time":69236,"text":"Let me start with the aspect"},{"time":70547,"text":"of comfort, because many people"},{"time":72253,"text":"are confusing"},{"time":75275,"text":"ambient temperature"},{"time":77429,"text":"with thermal comfort."}]},{"cues":[{"time":79157,"text":"We are used to looking at charts like"},{"time":80685,"text":"that, and you see this red line"},{"time":82676,"text":"showing the air temperature"},{"time":84028,"text":"in June and July, and yes, that's right,"},{"time":85510,"text":"it's picking up to 45 degrees C."},{"time":87781,"text":"It's actually very hot."},{"time":90621,"text":"But air temperature is not"},{"time":93140,"text":"the full set of climatic"},{"time":94741,"text":"parameters which define comfort."}]},{"cues":[{"time":97154,"text":"Let me show you analysis"},{"time":99045,"text":"a colleague of mine did looking"},{"time":102573,"text":"on different football, World Cups,"},{"time":105149,"text":"Olympic Games around the world,"},{"time":107061,"text":"looking on the comfort"},{"time":108357,"text":"and analyzing the comfort"},{"time":109788,"text":"people have perceived at these"},{"time":112588,"text":"different sport activities,"},{"time":114292,"text":"and let me start with Mexico."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116141,"text":"Mexico temperature has been, air"},{"time":117710,"text":"temperature has been something between"},{"time":119414,"text":"15, up to 30 degrees C, and people"},{"time":122461,"text":"enjoyed themselves."},{"time":124237,"text":"It was a very comfortable game"},{"time":126109,"text":"in Mexico City. Have a look."},{"time":128404,"text":"Orlando, same kind of stadium,"},{"time":130837,"text":"open-air stadium. People have"},{"time":133398,"text":"been sitting in the strong sun,"},{"time":136142,"text":"in the very high humidity"},{"time":137989,"text":"in the afternoon, and they"},{"time":139104,"text":"did not enjoy. It was not comfortable."},{"time":140910,"text":"The air temperature was not too high, but it was not"},{"time":142877,"text":"comfortable during these games."}]},{"cues":[{"time":145725,"text":"What about Seoul? Seoul, because"},{"time":147420,"text":"of broadcast rights, all the"},{"time":149852,"text":"games have been in the late"},{"time":151157,"text":"afternoon. Sun has already been"},{"time":152684,"text":"set, so the games have been"},{"time":155077,"text":"perceived as comfortable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":157637,"text":"What about Athens? Mediterranean"},{"time":160501,"text":"climate, but in the sun it was"},{"time":162790,"text":"not comfortable. They didn't perceive comfort."}]},{"cues":[{"time":165516,"text":"And we know that from Spain,"},{"time":167157,"text":"we know that \"sol y sombra.\""},{"time":169669,"text":"If you have a ticket, and you"},{"time":171837,"text":"get a ticket for the shade,"},{"time":173549,"text":"you pay more, because you're"},{"time":175757,"text":"in a more comfortable environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":179518,"text":"What about Beijing?"},{"time":180797,"text":"It's again, sun in the day"},{"time":183461,"text":"and high humidity,"},{"time":185189,"text":"and it was not comfortable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186452,"text":"So if I overlay, and if you"},{"time":187732,"text":"overlay all these comfort"},{"time":189421,"text":"envelopes, what we see is,"},{"time":191340,"text":"in all these places, air temperature has"},{"time":193596,"text":"been ranging something from 25"},{"time":197430,"text":"to 35, and if you go on"},{"time":199334,"text":"the line, 30, of 30 degrees C"},{"time":202093,"text":"ambient temperatures. If you"},{"time":203542,"text":"go along that line you see"},{"time":205195,"text":"there has been all kind of"},{"time":207716,"text":"comfort, all kinds of perceived"},{"time":209949,"text":"outdoor comfort, ranging from"},{"time":211758,"text":"very comfortable"},{"time":212943,"text":"to very uncomfortable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":214814,"text":"So why is that?"},{"time":217663,"text":"This is because there are"},{"time":219359,"text":"more parameters influencing"},{"time":221446,"text":"our thermal comfort, which is"},{"time":223352,"text":"the sun, the direct sun,"},{"time":225745,"text":"the diffuse sun, which is wind,"},{"time":228233,"text":"strong wind, mild wind, which is"},{"time":230921,"text":"air humidity, which is"},{"time":233207,"text":"the radiant temperature of the"},{"time":235436,"text":"surroundings where we are in."},{"time":237543,"text":"And this is air temperature."}]},{"cues":[{"time":239224,"text":"All these parameters go into"},{"time":240203,"text":"the comfort feeling of our"},{"time":242257,"text":"human body, and scientists"},{"time":243890,"text":"have developed a parameter,"},{"time":246243,"text":"which is the perceived"},{"time":247746,"text":"temperature, where all these"},{"time":249871,"text":"parameters go in and help"},{"time":252127,"text":"designers to understand"},{"time":255034,"text":"which is the driving parameter"},{"time":257168,"text":"that I feel comfort or that"},{"time":258800,"text":"I don't feel comfort."},{"time":260279,"text":"Which is the driving parameter"},{"time":261912,"text":"which gives me a perceived"},{"time":263264,"text":"temperature? And these parameters,"},{"time":265924,"text":"these climatic parameters are"},{"time":267592,"text":"related to the human metabolism."}]},{"cues":[{"time":271752,"text":"Because of our metabolism,"},{"time":273991,"text":"we as human beings,"},{"time":275944,"text":"we produce heat."},{"time":277584,"text":"I'm excited, I'm talking to you,"},{"time":279099,"text":"I'm probably producing"},{"time":280745,"text":"150 watts"},{"time":281856,"text":"at the moment. You are sitting,"},{"time":283192,"text":"you are relaxed, you're looking"},{"time":284880,"text":"at me. It's probably 100"},{"time":286227,"text":"watts each person is producing,"},{"time":288161,"text":"and we need to get rid of that"},{"time":290160,"text":"energy. I need, with my body,"},{"time":291911,"text":"to get rid of the energy, and"},{"time":293413,"text":"the harder it is for myself,"},{"time":295384,"text":"for my body, to get rid of the"},{"time":297464,"text":"energy, the less comfort I feel."},{"time":299703,"text":"That's it. And if I don't"},{"time":302019,"text":"get rid of the energy,"},{"time":303161,"text":"I will die."}]},{"cues":[{"time":304600,"text":"If we overlay what happens"},{"time":308952,"text":"during the football World Cup,"},{"time":311200,"text":"what will happen in June, July,"},{"time":312969,"text":"we will see, yes, air"},{"time":313896,"text":"temperature will be much higher,"},{"time":315776,"text":"but because the games and"},{"time":317432,"text":"the plays will be in the afternoon,"},{"time":319952,"text":"it's probably the same comfort"},{"time":321785,"text":"rating we've found in other"},{"time":323432,"text":"places which has perceived"},{"time":324928,"text":"as non-comfortable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":326639,"text":"So we sat together with a team"},{"time":328783,"text":"which prepared the Bid Book, or goal,"},{"time":331113,"text":"that we said, let's aim"},{"time":333888,"text":"for perceived temperature,"},{"time":335847,"text":"for outdoor comfort in this range,"},{"time":338490,"text":"which is perceived with a"},{"time":340161,"text":"temperature of 32 degrees"},{"time":343364,"text":"Celsius perceived temperature,"},{"time":344985,"text":"which is extremely comfortable."},{"time":347145,"text":"People would feel really fine"},{"time":349738,"text":"in an open outdoor environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":351632,"text":"But what does it mean?"},{"time":353591,"text":"If we just look on what happens,"},{"time":355640,"text":"we see, temperature's too high."},{"time":357751,"text":"If we apply the best architectural design,"},{"time":360544,"text":"climate engineering design,"},{"time":362008,"text":"we won't get much better."}]},{"cues":[{"time":364111,"text":"So we need to do something active."},{"time":366832,"text":"We need, for instance, to bring"},{"time":368702,"text":"in radiant cooling technology,"},{"time":370798,"text":"and we need to combine this"},{"time":372687,"text":"with so-called soft conditioning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374904,"text":"And how does it look like in a stadium?"},{"time":376340,"text":"So the stadium has a few"},{"time":378668,"text":"elements which create that"},{"time":380413,"text":"outdoor comfort. First of all,"},{"time":381655,"text":"it's shading. It needs"},{"time":383891,"text":"to protect where the people"},{"time":386205,"text":"are sitting against strong"},{"time":387869,"text":"and warm wind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":389068,"text":"But that's not all what we need"},{"time":390707,"text":"to do. We need to use"},{"time":393718,"text":"active systems."},{"time":395887,"text":"Instead of blowing a hurricane"},{"time":398327,"text":"of chilled air through the stadium,"},{"time":400702,"text":"we can use radiant"},{"time":402450,"text":"cooling technologies, like a"},{"time":404484,"text":"floor heating system where water"},{"time":406684,"text":"pipes are embedded in the floor."},{"time":409067,"text":"And just by using cold water"},{"time":410885,"text":"going through the water pipes,"},{"time":412213,"text":"you can release the heat"},{"time":413869,"text":"which is absorbed during the day"},{"time":415949,"text":"in the stadium, so you can"},{"time":417186,"text":"create that comfort, and then by"},{"time":419069,"text":"adding dry air instead of"},{"time":421629,"text":"down-chilled air, the spectators"},{"time":423861,"text":"and the football players can"},{"time":425743,"text":"adjust to their individual"},{"time":428076,"text":"comfort needs, to their"},{"time":429853,"text":"individual energy balance."},{"time":431509,"text":"They can adjust and find"},{"time":433486,"text":"their comfort they need to find."}]},{"cues":[{"time":435861,"text":"There are 12 stadia probably"},{"time":440317,"text":"to come, but there are"},{"time":442277,"text":"32 training pitches where"},{"time":444596,"text":"all the individual countries"},{"time":446293,"text":"are going to train."},{"time":447477,"text":"We applied the same concept:"},{"time":449374,"text":"shading of the training pitch,"},{"time":451604,"text":"using a shelter against wind,"},{"time":454444,"text":"then using the grass."},{"time":456333,"text":"Natural-watered lawn is a"},{"time":458853,"text":"very good cooling source"},{"time":460332,"text":"stabilizing temperature,"},{"time":461549,"text":"and using dehumidified air to"},{"time":463485,"text":"create comfort."}]},{"cues":[{"time":464564,"text":"But even the best passive design"},{"time":468438,"text":"wouldn't help."},{"time":469184,"text":"We need active system."},{"time":470194,"text":"And how do we do that?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":471244,"text":"Our idea for the bid was"},{"time":473612,"text":"100 percent solar cooling,"},{"time":475349,"text":"based on the idea that we use"},{"time":477444,"text":"the roof of the stadia,"},{"time":479084,"text":"we cover the roofs of the stadia"},{"time":481027,"text":"with PV systems."},{"time":482619,"text":"We don't borrow any energy"},{"time":485179,"text":"from history."},{"time":486603,"text":"We are not using fossil energies."},{"time":488396,"text":"We are not borrowing energy"},{"time":490212,"text":"from our neighbors."},{"time":491268,"text":"We're using energy we can harvest"},{"time":493388,"text":"on our roofs, and also on the"},{"time":496148,"text":"training pitches, which will be"},{"time":498235,"text":"covered with large, flexible"},{"time":500907,"text":"membranes, and we will see"},{"time":502620,"text":"in the next years an industry"},{"time":504324,"text":"coming up with flexible"},{"time":505507,"text":"photovoltaics, giving"},{"time":507132,"text":"the possibilities of shading"},{"time":508909,"text":"against strong sun and producing"},{"time":510589,"text":"electric energy in the same time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":513084,"text":"And this energy now is"},{"time":514795,"text":"harvested throughout the year,"},{"time":516427,"text":"sent into the grid,"},{"time":517995,"text":"is replacing fossils"},{"time":519980,"text":"in the grid, and when I need it"},{"time":522131,"text":"for the cooling, I take it"},{"time":525028,"text":"back from the grid and I"},{"time":526845,"text":"use the solar energy"},{"time":529212,"text":"which I have brought to the grid"},{"time":531284,"text":"back when I need"},{"time":532572,"text":"it for the solar cooling."},{"time":533404,"text":"And I can do that in the first"},{"time":534827,"text":"year and I can balance that"},{"time":535875,"text":"in the next 10, and the next"},{"time":537179,"text":"20 years, this energy,"},{"time":539044,"text":"which is necessary to condition"},{"time":541667,"text":"a World Cup in Qatar,"},{"time":543366,"text":"the next 20 years, this energy"},{"time":545325,"text":"goes into the grid of Qatar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":547906,"text":"So this -- (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":549119,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":550223,"text":"This is not only useful"},{"time":552904,"text":"for stadia. We can use that also"},{"time":554879,"text":"in open-air places and streets,"},{"time":557288,"text":"and we've been working on"},{"time":558471,"text":"the City of the Future"},{"time":559840,"text":"in Masdar, which is in the"},{"time":561227,"text":"United Emirates, Abu Dhabi."},{"time":562487,"text":"And I had the pleasure to work"},{"time":564199,"text":"on the central plaza."},{"time":565503,"text":"And the same idea to use there,"},{"time":567638,"text":"to create outdoor conditions"},{"time":569344,"text":"which are perceived"},{"time":570495,"text":"as comfortable. People enjoy"},{"time":571751,"text":"going there instead of going"},{"time":573951,"text":"into a shopping mall, which is"},{"time":575720,"text":"chilled down and which is"},{"time":576904,"text":"cooled. We wanted to create"},{"time":578983,"text":"an outdoor space"},{"time":580520,"text":"which is so comfortable that"},{"time":582487,"text":"people can go there in the"},{"time":584064,"text":"early afternoon, even in these"},{"time":586188,"text":"sunny and hot summer months,"},{"time":588180,"text":"and they can enjoy and meet there"},{"time":589526,"text":"with their families. (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":591332,"text":"And the same concept:"},{"time":592679,"text":"shade against the sun,"},{"time":594116,"text":"shade against the wind,"},{"time":595387,"text":"and use, use and take advantage"},{"time":599211,"text":"of the sun you can harvest"},{"time":601924,"text":"on your footprint."},{"time":603019,"text":"And these beautiful umbrellas."}]},{"cues":[{"time":605028,"text":"So I'd like to encourage you"},{"time":609316,"text":"to pay attention to your"},{"time":611684,"text":"thermal comfort, to your"},{"time":613348,"text":"thermal environment,"},{"time":614395,"text":"tonight and tomorrow,"},{"time":617084,"text":"and if you'd like to learn more"},{"time":618891,"text":"about that, I invite you"},{"time":620013,"text":"to go to our website."},{"time":621292,"text":"We uploaded a very simple"},{"time":623436,"text":"perceived temperature calculator"},{"time":625548,"text":"where you can check out"},{"time":626540,"text":"about your outdoor comfort."},{"time":627955,"text":"And I also hope that you"},{"time":631427,"text":"share the idea that"},{"time":632749,"text":"if engineers and designers"},{"time":634755,"text":"can use all these different"},{"time":636267,"text":"climatic parameters,"},{"time":638228,"text":"it will be possible to create"},{"time":641235,"text":"really good and comfortable"},{"time":644324,"text":"outdoor conditions,"},{"time":645604,"text":"to change our thermal perception"},{"time":648733,"text":"that we feel comfortable"},{"time":650611,"text":"in an outdoor environment,"},{"time":652699,"text":"and we can do that"},{"time":655091,"text":"with the best passive design,"},{"time":656955,"text":"but also using the energy source"},{"time":660131,"text":"of the site in Qatar which is"},{"time":663115,"text":"the sun."}]},{"cues":[{"time":663969,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":666485,"text":"Thank you very much. (Applause)"},{"time":668010,"text":"Shukran. (Applause)"}]}]}